    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Anvil Theatre &amp; Vancouver Independent Music Centre presents Goodbye, Strawberry Hill Saturday, May 2, 2026 | 7:30pm A concert celebrating the launch of Sharon Minemoto’s new album,&nbsp;Goodbye, Strawberry Hill&nbsp;(Cellar Music). This album tells her family’s stories, joyful and sad, from WWII to present day. Following the bombing of Pearl Harbour in December 1941, the Canadian [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
